829
00:47:49,566 --> 00:47:51,980
(humming)

830
00:47:51,980 --> 00:47:54,789
- Beautiful baby, and beautiful mother.

831
00:47:54,789 --> 00:47:55,710
(laughs)

832
00:47:55,710 --> 00:47:57,870
What is your little girl's name?

833
00:47:57,870 --> 00:47:58,870
- Arina.

834
00:47:58,870 --> 00:47:59,980
Aren't you, honey?

835
00:47:59,980 --> 00:48:00,920
Aren't you?

836
00:48:00,920 --> 00:48:02,870
- [Woman] You must be very proud.

837
00:48:02,870 --> 00:48:03,940
- Yes I am.

838
00:48:03,940 --> 00:48:06,240
I mean, we both are.

839
00:48:06,240 --> 00:48:07,550
- Is your husband?

840
00:48:07,550 --> 00:48:11,660
- He's overseas, far away in New Guinea.

841
00:48:11,660 --> 00:48:13,743
(laughs)

842
00:48:15,154 --> 00:48:18,071
(light jazz music)

843
00:48:23,250 --> 00:48:24,946
Hi Harriet.

844
00:48:24,946 --> 00:48:25,779
We're back.

845
00:48:26,640 --> 00:48:29,040
Arina and I had a lovely walk, didn't we?

846
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:30,570
Come on.

847
00:48:30,570 --> 00:48:32,510
Oh, oh, aww.

848
00:48:32,510 --> 00:48:34,628
We did, didn't we, we had a nice--

849
00:48:34,628 --> 00:48:35,461
(baby crying)

850
00:48:35,461 --> 00:48:36,294
Oh no.

851
00:48:36,294 --> 00:48:37,127
Look at your mommy.

852
00:48:39,030 --> 00:48:40,660
Don't cry.

853
00:48:40,660 --> 00:48:42,250
You know, I'll tend to her anytime,

854
00:48:42,250 --> 00:48:44,520
I mean I just love to, I do.

855
00:48:45,649 --> 00:48:47,120
How's tomorrow morning?

856
00:48:47,120 --> 00:48:49,260
Would that be all right?

857
00:48:49,260 --> 00:48:51,520
You know what, I'll see you
