2449
02:18:40,779 --> 02:18:42,620
I hope you're happy, Magda.

2450
02:18:43,890 --> 02:18:44,723
- [Norma Jeane] Happy?

2451
02:18:46,714 --> 02:18:47,764
- [Man] Your husband?

2452
02:18:50,390 --> 02:18:55,187
- My husband, is a good man.

2453
02:18:56,583 --> 02:18:58,290
- [Man] Oh Magda.

2454
02:18:58,290 --> 02:19:00,430
- Isaac, it's all right.

2455
02:19:01,795 --> 02:19:04,934
No more words.

2456
02:19:04,934 --> 02:19:07,990
Mr. Straussberg, excuse me,
can I do it again please,

2457
02:19:07,990 --> 02:19:09,890
