2458
02:19:10,994 --> 02:19:11,827
Just...

2459
02:19:17,300 --> 02:19:18,133
- Sure.

2460
02:19:23,469 --> 02:19:24,969
- [Man] Uh-oh, oh.

2461
02:19:25,901 --> 02:19:28,818
