winter here, freezing,

2491
02:21:03,950 --> 02:21:06,030
it wouldn't be hard to die, would it?

2492
02:21:07,810 --> 02:21:08,890
- Yes.

2493
02:21:08,890 --> 02:21:10,900
Well, about my play.

2494
02:21:13,160 --> 02:21:17,380
Magda is from a world
where people do freeze

2495
02:21:18,322 --> 02:21:20,331
during the winter.

2496
02:21:20,331 --> 02:21:22,990
She's a farm girl from Poland, a survivor.

2497
02:21:24,555 --> 02:21:28,270
I'm not sure that she
adds up for the audience.

2498
02:21:29,516 --> 02:21:33,240
- I have some ideas about Magda.

2499
02:21:33,240 --> 02:21:34,730
I mean, if you're interested.

2500
02:21:36,022 --> 02:21:37,372
- Of course I'm interested.

2501
02:21:38,570 --> 02:21:41,030
- This girl Magda, she's like the girl

2502
02:21:41,030 --> 02:21:43,450
in Chekhov's Three
Sisters, you know the girl

2503
02:21:43,450 --> 02:21:46,510
who marries the brother and
she has the sash on her dress

2504
02:21:46,510 --> 02:21:49,830
that isn't the right
color, only with Magda

2505
02:21:49,830 --> 02:21:52,060
