2530
02:23:17,800 --> 02:23:20,920
I mean, before it was
even born she loved it.

2531
02:23:20,920 --> 02:23:22,540
Isaac didn't know, nobody knew,

2532
02:23:22,540 --> 02:23:27,540
but she finds a man to marry
her so her baby could be born.

2533
02:23:29,720 --> 02:23:30,630
I'm sorry, it's...

2534
02:23:33,460 --> 02:23:35,860
- We don't have to talk
about the play, Marilyn.

2535
02:23:38,118 --> 02:23:39,560
I should call you Marilyn, shouldn't I?

2536
02:23:39,560 --> 02:23:41,230
Or is that a stage name?

2537
02:23:42,700 --> 02:23:45,910
- Well, you could call me
Norma, that's my real name.

2538
02:23:45,910 --> 02:23:47,560
- Somehow Norma doesn't suit you.

2539
02:23:48,420 --> 02:23:49,253
- It doesn't?

2540
02:23:50,590 --> 02:23:54,300
Norma Jeane is what my
mother called me, actually.

2541
02:23:54,300 --> 02:23:57,810
My mother, and my
father, it doesn't matter

2542
