2563
02:25:40,690 --> 02:25:42,160
- Hi, it's me.

2564
02:25:42,160 --> 02:25:42,993
Your Magda.

2565
02:25:44,110 --> 02:25:45,080
- Hey you.

2566
02:25:45,080 --> 02:25:45,980
- I had the power.

2567
02:25:47,300 --> 02:25:49,320
I would rewrite her story.

2568
02:25:49,320 --> 02:25:51,000
- I went to this tram bookshop today,

2569
02:25:51,000 --> 02:25:52,520
I bought those out of print plays of yours

2570
02:25:52,520 --> 02:25:54,800
that I hadn't read yet.

2571
02:25:54,800 --> 02:25:58,950
Your wonderful work, I admire you so much.

2572
02:25:58,950 --> 02:25:59,850
- I wanna see you.

2573
02:26:00,782 --> 02:26:04,050
