you in all my problems.

2574
02:26:04,050 --> 02:26:07,060
- [Woman] Anybody home?

2575
02:26:07,060 --> 02:26:09,400
- I'm on the phone, I'll be right there.

2576
02:26:09,400 --> 02:26:11,780
- I wanted to be a great actress for him,

2577
02:26:11,780 --> 02:26:12,980
