I wanted to die sometimes.

2580
02:26:20,710 --> 02:26:24,610
No, no, I wanted to live.

2581
02:26:24,610 --> 02:26:28,510
Just to live, and know
that he was living too.

2582
02:26:30,096 --> 02:26:32,660
Before you I wasn't anyone.

2583
02:26:32,660 --> 02:26:33,700
I wasn't even born.

2584
02:26:35,494 --> 02:26:39,440
There were other men, but you'll never

2585
02:26:39,440 --> 02:26:41,120
