2586
02:26:41,120 --> 02:26:41,953
About us?

2587
02:26:42,820 --> 02:26:45,847
When maybe you don't love me anymore?

2588
02:26:45,847 --> 02:26:47,184
- I'll always love you.

2589
02:26:47,184 --> 02:26:48,930
- But you're a writer.

2590
02:26:48,930 --> 02:26:52,676
First you see and then you write.

2591
02:26:52,676 --> 02:26:55,980
I mean, if we broke up.

2592
02:26:55,980 --> 02:26:59,250
- We won't break up.

2593
02:26:59,250 --> 02:27:03,473
- Other men, well that was
Marilyn Monroe, that wasn't me.

2594
02:27:04,400 --> 02:27:06,900
Most men I don't even feel
anything, but with you.

2595
02:27:08,000 --> 02:27:10,010
- I wish I didn't have to go to Tucson.

2596
02:27:10,010 --> 02:27:12,250
It just feels so far away.

2597
02:27:12,250 --> 02:27:13,620
- I know.

2598
02:27:13,620 --> 02:27:16,052
But we need money for your divorce.

2599
02:27:16,052 --> 02:27:16,952
I'm gonna convert.

2600
02:27:18,009 --> 02:27:21,021
I'm gonna un-baptize my
faith and become a Jew.

2601
02:27:21,021 --> 02:27:21,893
(both laugh)

2602
02:27:21,893 --> 02:27:22,993
In my soul I'm Jewish.

2603
02:27:24,760 --> 02:27:28,476
Let him kiss me with
the kisses of his mouth,

2604
02:27:28,476 --> 02:27:33,476
for thy love is better than wine.

2605
